entries.original: **Fully-qualified command names**: Documentation now uses `/oh-my-claudecode:omc-setup` and `/oh-my-claudecode:help` for namespace consistency
entries.translated: **정규화된 명령어 이름**: 문서에서는 이제 네임스페이스 일관성을 위해 `/oh-my-claudecode:omc-setup` 및 `/oh-my-claudecode:help`를 사용합니다.

entries.original: **Commands folder populated**: All user-facing commands now have full content (copied from skills)
entries.translated: **명령어 폴더 채워짐**: 모든 사용자 대상 명령어에 이제 전체 내용이 포함되었습니다 (기술에서 복사됨).

entries.original: **Separated commands vs skills**: - 20 commands (user-facing): analyze, cancel-ralph, cancel-ultraqa, cancel-ultrawork, deepinit, deepsearch, doctor, help, hud, learner, note, omc-setup, plan, ralph, ralph-init, ralplan, release, review, ultraqa, ultrawork - 6 skills-only (internal): orchestrate, frontend-ui-ux, git-master, omc-default, omc-default-global, planner
entries.translated: **명령어와 기술 분리**: - 20개의 명령어 (사용자 대상): analyze, cancel-ralph, cancel-ultraqa, cancel-ultrawork, deepinit, deepsearch, doctor, help, hud, learner, note, omc-setup, plan, ralph, ralph-init, ralplan, release, review, ultraqa, ultrawork - 6개의 기술 전용 (내부): orchestrate, frontend-ui-ux, git-master, omc-default, omc-default-global, planner

entries.original: **Consolidated planner into plan**: `planner` is now skill-only; users invoke via `/oh-my-claudecode:plan` ---
entries.translated: **planner를 plan으로 통합**: `planner`는 이제 기술 전용이며, 사용자는 `/oh-my-claudecode:plan`을 통해 호출합니다.
